code: @Override protected void doStart() throws Exception {     if (!hasThreadPool()) {         // if there is no thread pool then create a default thread pool using daemon threads with default size (200)         QueuedThreadPool qtp = new QueuedThreadPool().         qtp.setDaemon(true).         // let the thread names indicate they are from the client         qtp.setName("CamelJettyClient(" + ObjectHelper.getIdentityHashCode(this) + ")").         setThreadPoolOrExecutor(qtp).     }     super.doStart(). }
public abstract void setProxy(String host, int port).
public void setSupportRedirect(boolean supportRedirect) {     this.supportRedirect = supportRedirect. }
